<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Web Pages</title>
    <style>
        body{text-align:center;}
        table, th, td {border: 1px solid black; align:center;}
        .center {
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: auto;
        }
        #courseList{display: inline-block;text-align: left;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="background-color:lightgreen">
        <h1 id="table-heading">TABLES AND LISTS</h1><br>
        <table class="center" id="courseTable""width:50%">
        <tr><th>Roll No</th><th>Name</th><th>Course</th><th>Department</th></tr>
        <tr><td>101</td><td>ARUN</td><td>Computer</td><td>CS</td></tr>
        <tr><td>102</td><td>AJAY</td><td>Information Technology</td><td>IT</td></tr>
        <tr><td>103</td><td>BHAVANI</td><td>Mechanics</td><td>ME</td></tr>
        <tr><td>104</td><td>SARA</td><td>Electronics</td><td>EEE</td></tr>
        <tr><td>105</td><td>KEERTHANAA</td><td>artificial intelligence</td><td>AI</td></tr>
        <tr><td>106</td><td>ANIKA</td><td>communication</td><td>ECE</td></tr>
        </table><br>
        <h2 id="courseHeading">No Of Courses Available</h2>
        <ul id="courseList"><li>Computer Science</li><li>Electronics</li><li>Aerounetics</li><li>Mechanical</li><li>Artificial Intelligence</li></ul>
    </div>
        
    <div style="background-color:lightgreen">
        <h1 id="imageHeading">Image Map</h1>
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"alt="Workplace" usemap="#workmap" width="400" height="379">
        <map name="workmap">
          <area shape="rect" coords="34,44,270,350" alt="laptop" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laptop">
          <area shape="rect" coords="290,172,333,250" alt="Phone" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mobile_phone">
          <area shape="circle" coords="337,300,44" alt="Cup of coffee" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coffee">
        </map>
    </div>
        
    <div style="background-color:lightgreen">
        <h1>FILL THE FORM</h1>
        <form id="login-form">
        <label>Name :</label>
        <input type="text" id="fname"><br>
        <label>Password :</label>
        <input type="text"><br>
        <label>Email :</label>
        <input type="text"><br>
        <label for="courses">Courses :</label>
        <select name="Courses" id="course">
          <option value="Computer Science">Computer Science</option>
          <option value="IT">IT</option>
          <option value="ECE">ECE</option>
          <option value="EEE">EEE</option>
          <option value="AI">AI</option>
        </select><br>
        <label for="Address">Address :</label>
        <textarea id="Address" name="Address" rows="4" cols="50"></textarea><br>
        <label for="Country">Country :</label>
        <input list="Countries" name="Countries" id="Country">
        <datalist id="Countries">
          <option value="India">
          <option value="Sri Lanka">
          <option value="England">
          <option value="Germany">
          <option value="US">
        </datalist><br>
        <button id="submit_btn" type="submit" form="login-form" value="Submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </div>
        
    <div style="background-color:lightgreen">
        <h1 id="frameHeading">FRAMES IN HTML</h1><br>
        <iframe id="frameImage1" src="https://classroom.google.com/u/0/h"></iframe>
        <iframe id="frameImage2" src="https://www.skillrack.com/faces/ui/profile.xhtml;jsessionid=B13EA9D5AD2FFB3C9D82C45FEBD6ADA2"></iframe>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
